        "cooked": "<p>opened eagerly with hopes for a 2014-like experience, but this bottle, delicious though it was, didn\u2019t have the depth or acidity of its older brethren. A nice bottle of young white Burgundy, it will hopefully pick up some thickness and depth. It\u2019s perhaps a bit dilute compared to 14.</p>",
