        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/f/b77776/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-11-17T11:28:22.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Stop chasing 17 and buy more 14?</p>\n<p>Oddly enough received several offers on 2014 Ramonet for much less than 2017.</p>",
