        "created_at": "2019-11-17T13:13:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My experience with 2017 wb so far has primarily been at the Bourgogne level, which feels a step or so ahead of the 16s.  I didn\u2019t drink the young 14s so much so not sure how well they compare, though.</p>",
